sectionText: Title: Silius Italicus? Punica  Description: Reading of Silius Italicus? epic poem, the Punica, in Latin, with a focus on the language and style of Silius? poetry and the secondary literature on the poem, its characters, and various topics, such as the socio-politics of Imperial epic poetry, intertextuality, and gender.  Room location: 225 LIB
